        <div class="container section-padding-block">
            <h2 class="section-heading">Does This Sound Familiar?</h2>
            <div class="problem-grid">
                <div class="problem-item">
                    <div class="problem-icon">ü§î</div>
                    <p class="problem-text">
                        You have an idea but aren't sure if customers actually
                        want it or who your real target market is.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="problem-item">
                    <div class="problem-icon">üí∏</div>
                    <p class="problem-text">
                        You're afraid of wasting months and tens of thousands of
                        dollars building the wrong thing.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="problem-item">
                    <div class="problem-icon">üîÑ</div>
                    <p class="problem-text">
                        You skip validation and assume you understand your
                        customers, only to discover you don't.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="problem-item">
                    <div class="problem-icon">‚è≥</div>
                    <p class="problem-text">
                        You're debating internally about features instead of
                        letting customers tell you what matters.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 3: The Solution - Introduce Your "Bridge" -->
    <section class="solution-section">
        <div class="container section-padding-block">
            <h2 class="section-heading">
                Get Real Customer Validation and Tested Prototypes in Weeks
            </h2>
            <div class="solution-content">
                <div class="solution-main">
                    <h3 class="solution-title">Product Validation Sprints</h3>
                    <p class="solution-description">
                        Move from idea to validated, tested solution while
                        avoiding the costly mistake of building things nobody
                        wants. Get clear direction and tested solutions that
                        give you confidence to move forward‚Äîor smart reasons to
                        pivot before it's expensive.
                    </p>
                    <div class="solution-benefits">
                        <div class="benefit-item">
                            <span class="benefit-icon">‚úì</span>
                            <span class="benefit-text"
                                >Real customer validation, not assumptions or
                                internal team feedback</span
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div class="benefit-item">
                            <span class="benefit-icon">‚úì</span>
                            <span class="benefit-text"
                                >Technical + Product expertise with 8 years of
                                development experience</span
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div class="benefit-item">
                            <span class="benefit-icon">‚úì</span>
                            <span class="benefit-text"
                                >End-to-end process from customer discovery
                                through tested prototype</span
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 4: Who This Is For/Not For -->
    <section class="fit-section">
        <div class="container section-padding-block">
            <h2 class="section-heading">Is This Right for You?</h2>
            <div class="fit-grid">
                <div class="fit-card good-fit">
                    <h3 class="fit-title">This Is Perfect If You're:</h3>
                    <ul class="fit-list">
                        <li>
                            A startup founder with initial product concepts who
                            needs validation before development
