                            positioning
                        </li>
                        <li>Want to avoid costly pivots by validating early</li>
                        <li>
                            Looking for confidence in your product decisions
                            before major investment
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="fit-card not-fit">
                    <h3 class="fit-title">This Is NOT Right If:</h3>
                    <ul class="fit-list">
                        <li>
                            You need immediate development work (I focus on
                            validation before coding begins)
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            You already have a launched product with users
                            (you've moved beyond initial validation)
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            You want hands-off service (these are collaborative
                            processes that need your input)
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Your idea requires specialized technology (my
                            process works best for web and mobile applications)
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 5: The Services - Here's How We Do It -->
