                    <div class="service-header">
                        <h3 class="service-title">Customer Discovery Sprint</h3>
                        <div class="service-ideal">
                            <span class="service-ideal-label">Ideal For:</span>
                            <span class="service-ideal-text"
                                >Founders who need to validate the problem and
                                identify their target customer</span
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div class="service-meta">
                            <span class="service-duration">1 Week</span>
                            <span class="service-price">$1,500</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="service-outcomes">
                        <h4>What You Get:</h4>
                        <div class="outcome-item">
                            <span class="outcome-icon">‚úì</span>
                            <span class="outcome-text"
                                >Know if your idea is worth pursuing with clear
                                validation data</span
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div class="outcome-item">
                            <span class="outcome-icon">‚úì</span>
                            <span class="outcome-text"
                                >Discover your real target customer and stop
                                guessing</span
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div class="outcome-item">
                            <span class="outcome-icon">‚úì</span>
                            <span class="outcome-text"
                                >Understand the competitive landscape and gaps
                                you can win</span
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="service-deliverables">
                        <h4>Key Deliverable:</h4>
                        <div class="deliverable-item">
                            <span class="deliverable-icon">üìä</span>
                            <span class="deliverable-text"
                                >Customer Insights Report with go/no-go
                                recommendation</span
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="service-cta">
                        <a
                            href="https://cal.com/hanifcarroll/validation"
                            class="service-button">Learn More & Book</a
                        >
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Complete Validation Sprint -->
                <div class="service-card featured">
                    <div class="service-header">
                        <h3 class="service-title">
                            Complete Validation Sprint
                        </h3>
                        <div class="service-ideal">
                            <span class="service-ideal-label">Ideal For:</span>
                            <span class="service-ideal-text"
                                >Founders who have a defined problem and need to
                                validate the solution</span
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div class="service-meta">
                            <span class="service-duration">3-4 Weeks</span>
                            <span class="service-price">$4,000</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="service-outcomes">
                        <h4>What You Get:</h4>
                        <div class="outcome-item">
                            <span class="outcome-icon">‚úì</span>
                            <span class="outcome-text"
                                >Test your solution before building it with real
                                users</span
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div class="outcome-item">
                            <span class="outcome-icon">‚úì</span>
                            <span class="outcome-text"
                                >Know exactly what features matter based on
                                customer feedback</span
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div class="outcome-item">
                            <span class="outcome-icon">‚úì</span>
                            <span class="outcome-text"
                                >Get investor-ready validation with real user
                                feedback</span
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="service-deliverables">
                        <h4>Key Deliverables:</h4>
                        <div class="deliverable-item">
                            <span class="deliverable-icon">üíª</span>
                            <span class="deliverable-text"
                                >Working Prototype - Live demo link you can
                                share</span
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div class="deliverable-item">
                            <span class="deliverable-icon">üìã</span>
                            <span class="deliverable-text"
                                >Validation Results with user testing insights
                                and next steps</span
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="service-cta">
                        <a
                            href="https://cal.com/hanifcarroll/validation"
                            class="service-button primary">Learn More & Book</a
                        >
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Combined Package -->
            <div class="combined-package">
                <div class="package-card">
                    <div class="package-header">
                        <h3 class="package-title">Both Services Together</h3>
                        <div class="package-savings">Save $500</div>
                        <div class="package-meta">
                            <span class="package-duration">4-5 Weeks</span>
                            <span class="package-price">$5,000</span>
                            <span class="package-original"
                                >Originally $5,500</span
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="package-description">
                        <p>
                            Complete customer discovery plus validation testing.
                            Perfect for founders who need both market validation
                            and solution testing.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="package-cta">
                        <a
                            href="https://cal.com/hanifcarroll/validation"
                            class="service-button primary"
                            >Get Complete Validation</a
                        >
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 6: The Proof - Build Credibility with Case Studies -->
    <section class="proof-section">
        <div class="container section-padding-block">
            <h2 class="section-heading">See the Process in Action</h2>
            <div class="case-studies">
                <!-- Case Study 1: Language Exchange App -->
                <div class="case-study">
                    <div class="case-study-content">
                        <h3 class="case-study-title">
                            Language Exchange App Validation
                        </h3>
                        <div class="case-study-challenge">
                            <h4>Challenge:</h4>
                            <p>
                                A good idea (language exchange) with poor
                                execution by existing apps. Needed to validate
                                the concept and find the right approach.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="case-study-process">
                            <h4>My Process:</h4>
                            <p>
                                I interviewed 20+ locals in Buenos Aires,
                                prototyped the core experience, and tested it
                                with real users in under two weeks.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="case-study-solution">
                            <h4>Solution:</h4>
                            <p>
                                Customer insights completely changed the product
                                direction. I designed and built a functional
                                prototype to test with real users, uncovering
                                critical insights‚Äîlike the need for real
                                photos‚Äîbefore any production code was written.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="case-study-result">
                            <h4>Result:</h4>
                            <p>
                                A validated concept with clear direction that
                                saved months of wrong development and thousands
                                in development costs.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="case-study-links">
                            <a
                                href="/projects/language-exchange"
                                class="case-study-link"
                            >
                                View Full Case Study ‚Üí
                            </a>
