    <section class="why-me-section">
        <div class="container section-padding-block">
            <h2 class="section-heading">Your Technical Co-Pilot</h2>
            <div class="why-me-content">
                <div class="why-me-photo">
                    <img
                        src="/img/portrait-professional-desktop.webp"
                        alt="Hanif Carroll - Professional headshot"
                        class="professional-photo"
                    />
                </div>
                <div class="why-me-bio">
                    <p class="bio-experience">
                        With 8 years in product development, I've seen firsthand
                        how great ideas fail due to skipping validation and
                        building the wrong things.
                    </p>
                    <p class="bio-why">
                        I focus on validation before coding begins because my
                        passion is ensuring we're building the right things, not
                        just building things right.
                    </p>
                    <p class="bio-values">
                        My approach combines technical expertise with deep UX
                        understanding, using real customer validation instead of
                        assumptions or internal team feedback.
                    </p>
                    <p class="bio-personal">
                        When I'm not doing this, I'm building community here in
                        Buenos Aires, connecting people, and exploring how to
                        live a good life‚Äîvalues that I bring to every project.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 8: The Final CTA - Make the Decision Easy -->
    <section class="final-cta-section">
        <div class="container section-padding-block">
            <div class="final-cta-content">
                <h2 class="final-cta-title">
                    Ready to Validate with Confidence?
                </h2>
                <p class="final-cta-description">
                    Stop guessing. A 30-minute call is all it takes to get
                    clarity on your next steps. We'll discuss your idea,
                    identify your biggest risks, and determine if a validation
                    sprint is the right fit for you. No pressure, no strings
                    attached.
                </p>
                <a
                    href="https://cal.com/hanifcarroll/validation"
                    class="cta-button primary large"
                >
                    Schedule Your Free 30-Minute Validation Call
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 9: FAQ - Overcome Objections -->
    <section class="faq-section">
        <div class="container section-padding-block">
            <h2 class="section-heading">A Few Common Questions</h2>
            <div class="faq-list">
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3 class="faq-question">What happens after the sprint?</h3>
                    <p class="faq-answer">
                        My goal is to leave you with a validated plan and tested
                        prototype you can act on. While I don't offer full-stack
                        development, I can provide guidance on the hiring
                        process and help you avoid common pitfalls when bringing
                        on technical talent.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3 class="faq-question">
                        Why not just hire a freelance developer and start
                        building?
                    </h3>
                    <p class="faq-answer">
                        A freelance developer will build what you ask them to. I
                        help you figure out what you should be asking for in the
                        first place. This validation process happens before
                        development to ensure you don't waste your investment
                        building the wrong thing.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3 class="faq-question">
                        How do you work around my schedule?
                    </h3>
                    <p class="faq-answer">
                        I offer flexible scheduling that works around your
                        availability while maintaining momentum and
                        effectiveness. We'll establish a cadence that fits your
                        schedule during our initial call.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3 class="faq-question">Is my idea safe?</h3>
                    <p class="faq-answer">
                        Absolutely. Our engagement is built on trust. I'm happy
                        to sign a Non-Disclosure Agreement (NDA) before our
                        first call to ensure your intellectual property is
                        protected.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3 class="faq-question">
                        Do you have a money-back guarantee?
                    </h3>
                    <p class="faq-answer">
                        Due to the hands-on, consultative nature of the work, I
                        don't offer refunds once a sprint has begun. However,
                        the purpose of our initial free call is to ensure we are
                        a perfect fit and that I am completely confident I can
                        deliver value to you.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
